    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to the pan and stir until fully combined</p><p>Stir in the <strong>beef stock</strong> and your <strong>mint sauce</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>lamb mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1519.-step-5-x200.jpg",
