            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1519.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, allow the <strong>minty shepherd's pie</strong> to cool slightly (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>minty shepherd's pie </strong>with the <strong>leek &</strong> <strong>courgette</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
